        <p>They say you only turn 30 once. This is very true, and you have to do something special to celebrate it. For me, this entailed going to the Grand Canyon, one of the most beautiful places in the United States. How did I decide on going
            to the Grand Canyon? Let's review the decision process.</p>
        <p>As you may or may not know, my first idea to celebrate my 30th birthday was to go to Los Angeles, where I've never had a birthday, while Jenn had her 8th birthday with the family down there. As time went on, I realized it was difficult
