        <p>Within my list, I had the places I would absolutely kill to see, and others that could wait down the road. After reviewing the list, I came down to two finalists. The Grand Canyon was one, the other one was Yosemite National Park.</p>
        <p>What made me choose Grand Canyon over Yosemite? For starters, Grand Canyon is considered to be an experience of a lifetime, one that a special birthday deserves. Yosemite National Park is another amazing place, with beautiful waterfalls,
